text.tspan: Quest'opera stata identificata come libera da restrizioni

Esta obra ha sido identificada como libre de restricciones conocidas
en virtud de las leyes de derechos de autor, incluidos todos los derechos relacionados y auxiliares.
This work has been identified as being free of known restrictions under copyright law,
including all related and neighboring rights.
